{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place coriander seeds, cumin seeds and dried red chillies into mixing bowl and toast <b>5 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Grind <b>1 min\/speed 8<b>.","Add fresh coriander, garlic, ginger and olive oil then blend <b>1 min\/speed 10<b>. Scrape down sides and lid of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add water, lemon juice, salt, dried onions, tomato purée and turmeric then cook <b>45 min\/80°C\/speed 2<b>.","Transfer to sterilized jars, adding a little olive oil to cover the paste. Seal jars with sterilized lids and store in refrigerator until needed."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["40 g coriander seeds","40 g cumin seeds","10 g dried red chillies","50 g fresh coriander, leaves and stalks","100 g garlic cloves","100 g fresh ginger, peeled, cut into slices (2 mm)","220 g olive oil","100 g water","100 g lemon juice","30 g salt","50 g dried onions              (optional)","140 g tomato purée (concentrated)","1 heaped tsp ground turmeric"]}],"id":"r168174","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-po5qQazM-o8\/XZadHYyhn6I\/AAAAAAAAgYc\/vb9e8yauOD40nOkXhpFD7OjeMr9SRkwygCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_3ugBuI14g_jEF8bN.png","title":"Tikka paste","publishedAt":"2018-10-15T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"19.3 g","fat":"264.6 g","uom":"per 1 Complete recipe","carbohydrates":"114.9 g","calories":"12209 kJ \/ 2918 kcal"},"usefulItems":"sterilised jars, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Top up with a little more oil after each use so the paste stays submerged; this helps to preserve it.","To make a smaller quantity, halve the ingredients and cook for <b>25 minutes<b> in <b>step 3<b>."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h","1"]}